title: CodeX 2019 Inter-SHS Programming Competition
description: March 1, 2019 - MCL-ACM held their very first Inter-SHS Programming Competition with six participating schools. The first place, second place and third place were won by Laguna College of Business and Arts, Sto. Domingo Integrated High School, and STI College - Sta. Cruz respectively. Other schools that participated were Christ the King College of Science and Technology, Mind and Integrity College Inc. and Carmona Senior Highschool.
summary: MCL-ACM held their very first Inter-SHS Programming Competition with six participating schools.
